Class ActivityResources

  • java.lang.Object
    • economico.ActivityResources

  • public class ActivityResources
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains the recourses to manipulate the objects which are into an ArrayList parameterized with Activity.

      • getByIndicator

        public java.util.ArrayList<Activity> getByIndicator(java.util.ArrayList<Activity> activities,
                                                    java.lang.String indicator)
        This method filter the activities by looking for an indicator. If the indicator match with the indicators into the Activity class, it will be stored into another ArrayList and finally returns it.
        Parameters:
        activities - The ArrayList parameterized with Activity class who contains the information to be filtered.
        indicator - The indicator to compare with.
        Returns:
        An ArrayList parameterized with Activity which contains the activities filtered.

      • getByCountries

        public java.util.ArrayList<Activity> getByCountries(java.util.ArrayList<Activity> activities,
                                                    java.util.ArrayList<java.lang.String> countries)
        This method filter the activities by looking for countries. If the country (or countries) match with the country into the Activity class, it will be stored into another ArrayList and finally returns it.
        Parameters:
        activities - The ArrayList parameterized with Activity class who contains the information to be filtered.
        countries - The ArrayList parameterized with Country to compare with.
        Returns:
        An ArrayList parameterized with Activity which contains the activities filtered.
        See Also:
        Country

      • getByYears

        public java.util.ArrayList<Coords> getByYears(Activity activity,
                                              java.lang.Integer minValue,
                                              java.lang.Integer maxValue)
        This method filter the data organized by years from an Activity class.
        Parameters:
        activity - A specific Activity class to be filtered.
        minValue - The year since the information will be filtered.
        maxValue - The year until the information will be filtered.
        Returns:
        An ArrayList parameterized with Coords class as Year and data respectively.
